**Positive patterns:**
- ✅ `AsSpan`-based concatenation in `FixedLengthTruncator` left-path (L65-67) and `FixedNumberOfCharactersTruncator` (L134, L148)
- ✅ Null-coalescing for `truncationString` avoids repeated null checks
- ✅ Early returns for null/empty/within-length inputs avoid unnecessary work
